{"text": "def minimum_spanning_tree(weight_by_edge):\n    group_by_node = {}\n    mst_edges = set()\n\n    for edge in sorted(weight_by_edge, key=weight_by_edge.__getitem__):\n        u, v = edge\n        if group_by_node.setdefault(u, {u}) != group_by_node.setdefault(v, {v}):\n            mst_edges.add(edge)\n            group_by_node[u].update(group_by_node[v])\n            for node in group_by_node[v]:\n                group_by_node[node].update(group_by_node[u])\n\n    for edge in mst_edges:\n        u, v = edge\n        yield edge\n\n    return mst_edges", "parts": ["def minimum_spanning_tree(weight_by_edge):\n    group_by_node = {}\n    mst_edges = set()\n\n    for edge in sorted(weight_by_edge, key=weight_by_edge.__getitem__):\n        u, v = edge\n        if group_by_node.setdefault(u, {u}) != group_by_node.setdefault(v, {v}):\n            mst_edges.add(edge)\n            group_by_node[u].update(group_by_node[v])\n            for node in group_by_node[v]:\n                ", "\n\n    return mst_edges"], "infills": ["group_by_node[node].update(group_by_node[u])\n\n    for edge in mst_edges:\n        u, v = edge\n        yield edge"], "retries_attempted": 1}